Devolution CS Mwangi Kiunjuri has accused NASA presidential candidate Raila Odinga of seeking political mileage with the unga issue.The CS said events that led to the shortage of maize in the country was a natural phenomena. He said drought and famine are global issues. &ldquo;It is therefore irresponsible, unfortunate and really unacceptable that opposition leaders have sought to discredit government efforts,&rdquo; he said.He spoke on Tuesday at the Kenya Ports Authority, when he flagged off a consignment of 155,000 bags of rice.The consignment was from China and will be distributed for free distribution across the country. &ldquo;Don&rsquo;t squeeze some political mileage out of it,&rdquo; Kiunjuri said.